	   <tr><td colspan=2>I sat at +1200 +1300 faced East just like was posted was awesome amount of help.  <br>I sat from 6am till about 9am I would kill the Giant Wasp Place holder every 30mins and just let my necro stand there while I went and did the dishes vacumed, and what ever else.  Every 30mins I come back and kill the Giant Wasp and then go and do something, I got smart and decided to log every 30mins right at +1200 +1300.  It took me roughly 6-7 real hours of doing this and she eventually popped up.  When she did pop I was completely suprised, because her name was Alania not Alcia.  Its amazing how fast she ran, was like a virgin hillbilly girl running from her horny brothers and father.  Once I got dooming on her and sent my pet on her I already had her down to 75% of her life.  Make sure to get fear on her as soon as possible she likes to nuke for 200-300 right off the bat, wicked druid bitch.  She killed my pet first round I ran back to near +1200 +1300 Feigned Death and she left me alone, I was low on mana and pretty good on health 1200hp or so.  It just so happened that a Chanter friend of mine Maggikdagger was in the zone, I asked him to come help me really fast, he asked me what faction hit there was I told him most likely druid faction and he still came to help me out what a friend.  Well I was very low on mana and I knew he would be here any sec and I wanted to kill her before she despawned on me.  So I got brave and refused to go quitely into the night, I had about 1 blue bub of mana left after casting my 49pet and she was ready for me, she was blasting me before I had even gotten my pet out, but then my super erudite necro stanima kicked in and I held my ground, my pet came to me and attacked the evil druid bitch, whacking her and beating her down good.  I threw dooming darkness on her and fear.  Quickly I pulled out Lich and started pumping for mana, right about then Maggikdagger came and started to blast her with his Chanter spells, I followed close behind praying that the other druid would not come by and whack me around.  I was exhausted and my pet was still on her, she was strong enough to finally get rid of my dooming darkness but it was too late, the blasts of nukes and my pet cutting up her firm well shaped legs and slashing at her with fierce and menacing blows to her butt, pulling her hair back and landing blow after blow finally she gave in and fell to the ground exhausted from the onslaught of the greatest mind blow she may ever have had.  Oh and she resists poison alot, I dont recommened even having it up as a spell against her just keep tapping her life and fearing her with snares, she is very east to bring down to her knees, you just have to have the right stuff for her to do it.  I could have done it solo easy but I was just very surprised and jumpy at the thought that I was one step closer to finishing this damn quest, but with the low mana I had Maggikdagger was a great deal of help.  Oh and she has a very pretty druid heart, I rub it and lick it right before I go to bed at night now, I sometimes put it down my shorts and...you fill in the blanks.<br><br>Good luck guys im off to everfrost now to kill the dark assassin lets see if he gives it up for me so I can finally finish this damn thing and get rid of my crappy +5int rings<br><br>The YOYOMAN<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
